cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the segmentation of retinal blood vessels from fundus images. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The structured prediction approach used in the paper could also place it in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the use of fundus images suggests that it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
